title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Proceeds from sales of carved ducks go to handicap children.” [A sign in a Greek pizeria in Peabody, Massachusetts. Submitted by Nell Wright, Lynnfield, Massachusetts.]
